Description: fast radio interferometric calibration routines
 CubiCal implements several accelerated gain solvers which exploit complex
 optimisation. Computationally intensive functions have been Cythonised to
 further accelerate them and multiprocessing is fully supported.
 .
 This package installs the library for Python 2.

